### Configure Live Preview for Pages Collection - TypeScript

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/examples/live-preview/README.md

Configuration to enable Live Preview in the pages collection using the admin.livePreview property. The url function generates the preview URL dynamically based on the page slug, allowing real-time rendering of the front-end within the admin panel.

```typescript
// ./src/collections/Pages.ts
{
  // ...
  admin: {
    livePreview: {
      url: ({ data }) => `${process.env.PAYLOAD_URL}/${data.slug}`
    }
  }
}
```

