### Custom Textarea Field Server Component (React/TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/payloadcms/payload/blob/main/docs/fields/textarea.mdx

This code defines a custom server component for a Textarea Field using React and TypeScript. It imports necessary types and components from '@payloadcms/ui' and 'payload', rendering the default TextareaField with provided props. This is useful for extending or customizing field behavior on the server.

```tsx
import type React from 'react'
import { TextareaField } from '@payloadcms/ui'
import type { TextareaFieldServerComponent } from 'payload'

export const CustomTextareaFieldServer: TextareaFieldServerComponent = ({ 
  clientField,
  path,
  schemaPath,
  permissions,
}) => {
  return (
    <TextareaField
      field={clientField}
      path={path}
      schemaPath={schemaPath}
      permissions={permissions}
    />
  )
}
```

